components_any <- 
  components_any %>%
  left_join(total_pm2.5, by = "date_local") %>%
  select(date_local: pm2.5_total)

PCA any

components_any <- 
  components_any %>% 
  select(-date_local, -pm2.5_total)

pca_any <- 
  prcomp(components_any)

summary(pca_any)
## Importance of components:
##                           PC1    PC2     PC3     PC4     PC5     PC6     PC7
## Standard deviation     2.9808 1.5436 0.15302 0.06882 0.03821 0.02984 0.01886
## Proportion of Variance 0.7863 0.2109 0.00207 0.00042 0.00013 0.00008 0.00003
## Cumulative Proportion  0.7863 0.9972 0.99929 0.99971 0.99984 0.99992 0.99995
##                            PC8     PC9     PC10     PC11    PC12     PC13
## Standard deviation     0.01595 0.01233 0.009551 0.006443 0.00538 0.002699
## Proportion of Variance 0.00002 0.00001 0.000010 0.000000 0.00000 0.000000
## Cumulative Proportion  0.99997 0.99998 0.999990 0.999990 1.00000 1.000000
##                            PC14     PC15     PC16    PC17     PC18    PC19
## Standard deviation     0.002533 0.002334 0.002234 0.00192 0.001799 0.00111
## Proportion of Variance 0.000000 0.000000 0.000000 0.00000 0.000000 0.00000
## Cumulative Proportion  1.000000 1.000000 1.000000 1.00000 1.000000 1.00000
##                             PC20      PC21
## Standard deviation     0.0006602 0.0005591
## Proportion of Variance 0.0000000 0.0000000
## Cumulative Proportion  1.0000000 1.0000000
pca_any$rotation %>% 
  as_tibble() %>% 
  mutate(Chemicals = colnames(components_any)) %>% 
  select(Chemicals, PC1:PC6) %>% 
  gather(key = Component, value = Loadings, -Chemicals) %>%
  mutate(Chemicals = fct_inorder(Chemicals)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Chemicals, y = Loadings)) + geom_point() +
  geom_segment(aes(yend=0, xend = Chemicals)) +
  facet_wrap(.~Component) + theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1),
        legend.position = "bottom",
        strip.background = element_blank())

scores_pca <- pca_any$x

summary statistics and visualizations

PCA_any <- pca_any$sdev^2/sum(pca_any$sdev^2) *100
PCA_all <- pca_any$sdev^2/sum(pca_all$sdev^2) *100
PCA_124 <- pca_any$sdev^2/sum(pca_124$sdev^2) *100
round(cbind(Component = 1:21, PCA_any, PCA_all, PCA_124), 4) %>% kable()
